      "author": "nicolasassi",
      "description": "Initial release as **Redline**.\n\n## Features\n\n- Add PR-style review comments anchored to any block (paragraph, heading, list item, image, code block, callout, table)\n- Sidecar markdown file (`<doc>.review.md`) keeps source documents clean\n- Editor gutter markers (open / resolved / stale)\n- Right-side review sidebar with filters and per-comment actions\n- Automatic stale-anchor detection on file open\n- Per-document or central-folder sidecar storage\n\nSee [README](https://github.com/nicolasassi/redline/blob/main/README.md) and the [sidecar format spec](https://github.com/nicolasassi/redline/blob/main/docs/format-spec.md).",
